@baseUrl = http://192.168.2.4:8080
@json = application/json

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Submit a time (best time kept per group_key + map_id + account_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/times
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
	"group_key": "friends1",
	"account_id": "55c18e06-1001-4fee-aab2-ed8b6798e340",
	"map_id": "kZoyOAR0_D_tUd1ZlOO4GaC3BI6",
	"time_ms": 16873
}

### Submit another time for the same player (should keep the lower/best time)
POST {{baseUrl}}/times
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
	"group_key": "friends1",
	"account_id": "acc_123",
	"map_id": "map_A",
	"time_ms": 70000
}

### Submit a second player for the same group + map
POST {{baseUrl}}/times
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
	"group_key": "friends1",
	"account_id": "acc_456",
	"map_id": "map_A",
	"time_ms": 60000
}

### Get leaderboard for a group + map (default limit=50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard?group_key=friends1&map_id=map_A

### Get leaderboard with explicit limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard?group_key=friends1&map_id=map_A&limit=10

